cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.DS

This paper deals with natural language processing and machine learning techniques applied to the Czech language. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also uses word embeddings, which are a popular tool in machine learning, making cs.LG (Machine Learning) another likely category. Additionally, the paper involves unsupervised clustering, which falls under the category of unsupervised learning, making cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) a possible category. The paper also deals with large datasets and network structures, which could fall under cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). Finally, the paper involves data analysis and processing, which could fall under cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms).
